job.title: Software Engineer
job.description: This is what you'll do: Help define roadmap and architecture based on technology and business needs. Create applications for both production clients and machine learning researchers. Write well-crafted, well-tested, readable, maintainable code. Collaborate with other engineers to deliver state of the art solutions.<br><br>This would be good to know about: Experience working at an early stage startup. Experience in a HIPAA compliant environment. Experience working on machine learning or healthcare related projects. Experience taking ownership of projects.<br><br>The salary range for this position is $100,000 - $155,000
